snippet.title: The Third Wish - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Third Wish is a sci-fi point & click adventure about a family and fate and consequence. Full voice acting by Travis Baldree.

Made in two weeks for Adventure Jam 2023. https://georgebroussard.itch.io/the-third-wish
